      • accessKeys

        CallTarget accessKeys()
        Handles request for access to a message not known in version 0.10. The parameter to the returned CallTarget is going to be the object/receiver. The return value is supposed to be a TruffleObject that represents an array (responds to Message.HAS_SIZE and Message.GET_SIZE and its element represent String names of properties of the receiver.
        Returns:
        call target to handle the message or null if this message is not supported
        Since:
        0.18
